  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "Tac-Kek JayPC 插板胸挂（黑色）",
      "en": "Tac-Kek JayPC plate carrier (Black)"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "JayPC",
      "en": "JayPC"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "Crye Precision JPC 插板胸挂的廉价仿制品，水弹玩家下场专用。虽然穿着舒适性不如原版 JPC，但仍然具备基础的改装能力。看样子装备的前任主人只加挂了最基础的副包，以最大限度保持机动能力。",
      "en": "A cheap airsoft bootleg of the Crye Precision JPC plate carrier. Doesn't offer the comfort of the original JPC, but retains extensive customization options. It looks like the previous owner chose not to overload the carrier with pouches to stay as mobile as possible."
    },
